384
00:32:57,040 --> 00:32:58,314
Grave, sí, grave.

385
00:33:01,240 --> 00:33:03,595
Vamos a Jerusalén...

386
00:33:03,720 --> 00:33:06,632
Sí. Vamos.
Cenar en Jerusalén.

387
00:33:11,600 --> 00:33:13,477
